{"type":null,"faqId":44734,"title":"如何启用PIN码锁定屏幕？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.\t设置&gt;隐身和安全&gt;安全&gt;加密&gt;加密手机&gt;PIN。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.\t在“选择你的PIN”下面的提示框中输入PIN码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.\t再次输入刚才输入的PIN码，点击确定完成对PIN码的设定。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">当点电源键或开关机时，手机会默认进入PIN码解锁界面，输入设定的PIN码后点击“OK”解除PIN码的锁定。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=160986\" style=\"width:1.7659723in;height:3.1194444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s1\"> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=160987\" style=\"width:1.74375in;height:3.1194444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s1\"> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=160988\" style=\"width:1.74375in;height:3.1194444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"235","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode